OL,3,CSaudi Arabia officially announced as
OL,4,C2034 World Cup host
OL,6,FThe Gulf kingdom has been seen as the
OL,7,Fde facto host since October 2023, when
OL,8,FAustralia pulled out of the running
OL,9,Fafter Fifa gave them less than four
OL,10,Fweeks to declare their bid.
OL,12,FFifa's member nations voted at the
OL,13,Fsame time to award the 2030 World Cup
OL,14,Fto Morocco, Spain and Portugal, in the
OL,15,Ffirst uncontested bidding process for
OL,16,Fmore than half a century.
OL,18,FGianni Infantino, Fifa's president,
OL,19,Fhailed the decision as a "historic
OL,20,Fcompromise" that "unites the world."
