OL,6,F"I fully trust our hosts to address
OL,7,Fall open points in this process and
OL,8,Fdeliver a World Cup that meets the
OL,9,Fworld's expectations," he said.
OL,11,FHuman rights groups have sharply
OL,12,Fcriticised the decision to award
OL,13,Ffootball's biggest prize to Saudi
OL,14,FArabia, warning that thousands of
OL,15,Fmigrant workers will die building
OL,16,Fstadiums, hotels and roads to
OL,17,Faccommodate hundreds of thousands of
OL,18,Ffans.
