OL,6,FLina al-Hathloul, a Saudi human rights
OL,7,Factivist, told ITV News that Fifa
OL,8,Fshould have used the award of the
OL,9,Ftournament to incentivise reform in
OL,10,Fthe kingdom.
OL,12,F"We want Fifa to condition it to the
OL,13,Frelease of political prisoners. We
OL,14,Fwant it to be conditional on the
OL,15,Flifting of travel bans, ending the
OL,16,Fdeath penalty, and bringing in human
OL,17,Frights organisations on the ground,"
OL,18,Fshe said.
