OL,6,FThe English Football Association
OL,7,Fbacked the Saudi bid, saying it
OL,8,Freceived ''assurances'' that LGBTQ+
OL,9,Ffans would be ''safe and welcome.''
OL,11,F"The FA Board met the Saudi Arabian
OL,12,FFootball Federation last month to
OL,13,Fdiscuss their bid in more detail," the
OL,14,FFA said in a statement.
