OL,6,F"We asked them to commit to ensuring
OL,7,Fall fans would be safe and welcome in
OL,8,FSaudi Arabia in 2034 ` including
OL,9,FLGBTQ+ fans. They assured us that they
OL,10,Fare fully committed to providing a
OL,11,Fsafe and welcome environment for all
OL,12,Ffans.''
OL,14,FBefore the 2022 World Cup in
OL,15,Fneighbouring Qatar, the FA was one of
OL,16,Ften European Football Associations to
OL,17,Fpress Fifa to create a compensation
OL,18,Ffund for migrant workers and to
OL,19,Frespect human rights and the safety of
OL,20,FLGBTQ+ fans.
