OL,6,FAhead of Wednesday's online meeting,
OL,7,Fthe Norwegian Football Federation
OL,8,F(NFF) criticised the "flawed and
OL,9,Finconsistent" bidding process, writing
OL,10,Fto Fifa to demand "greater
OL,11,Ftransparency, fairness, and stricter
OL,12,Fadherence to Fifa's 2016 reforms".
OL,14,FResponding to the NFF's letter,
OL,15,FMattias Grafstrom, Fifa Secretary
OL,16,FGeneral, promised to address all
OL,17,Fcomplaints after the congress.
