OL,6,FThe government of Saudi Arabia has
OL,7,Fpreviously said the kingdom was
OL,8,F"committed to safeguarding workers'
OL,9,Frights and combating forced labour.
OL,10,FAll workplace incidents are thoroughly
OL,11,Finvestigated. Deaths are handled in
OL,12,Fline with international standards and
OL,13,Ffree healthcare is provided to
OL,14,Feveryone in critical situations."
OL,16,FSaudi Arabia is investing heavily in
OL,17,Fglobal sport, and the Saudi Crown
OL,18,FPrince, Mohammed bin Salman, known by
OL,19,Fhis initials MBS, has established a
OL,20,Fclose relationship with Fifa President
OL,21,FGianni Infantino.
